<p><a name="Running" id="Running"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Marathon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Running">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Running</span></h2>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox ambox-content" style="">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image">
<div style="width: 52px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ambox_content.png" class="image" title="Ambox content.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/f4/Ambox_content.png" width="40" height="40" border="0" /></a></div>
</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>contains <a href="/wiki/Category:Articles_containing_how-to_sections" title="Category:Articles containing how-to sections">instructions, advice, or how-to content</a></b>. The purpose of Wikipedia is to present facts, not to train. Please help <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Marathon&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Marathon&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve this article</a> either by rewriting the how-to content or by <a href="http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Transwiki" class="extiw" title="m:Help:Transwiki">moving</a> it to <a href="http://en.wikiversity.org/wiki/" class="extiw" title="v:">Wikiversity</a> or <a href="http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/" class="extiw" title="b:">Wikibooks</a>.</td>
